# Employee Salary Prediction Pipeline

This project predicts employee salary using Machine Learning Pipeline in Scikit-learn.

## Features
- Missing value handling
- Feature scaling
- Pipeline implementation
- ColumnTransformer
- Linear Regression model

## Evaluation Metrics
- MAE
- RMSE
- R² Score

## Libraries Used
- pandas
- numpy
- scikit-learn
- joblib

## Files
- Salary.csv
- train_pipeline.ipynb
- predict_salary.ipynb
- salary_pipeline.pkl
